      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>wholewheat noodles</strong> to a pot and cover them with<strong> boiled water</strong> until fully submerged</p>\n<p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p>\n<p>Once tender, drain the <strong>noodles</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong></p>\n<p>Tip: drizzle over a little vegetable oil to stop the noodles from sticking <span class=\"text-highlight\">together</span></p>",
