    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained noodles</strong>, <strong>crispy pork</strong> and <strong>spicy sesame sauce</strong> to the pan with the <strong>wilted spring greens</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>spicy pork &amp; sesame noodles</strong></p>\n<p>Tip: add a splash more <span class=\"text-highlight\">starchy noodle water</span> if the sauce is looking a little <span class=\"text-highlight\">dry</span></p>\n<p> </p>",
